org.apache.ambari.server.api.predicate

Class QueryLexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.api.predicate.QueryLexer

  • public class QueryLexer
extends Object
    Scans a query expression and generates an array of tokens. Each token contains type and value information. First, the query expression is broken down into string tokens using a regular expression which splits on a set of deliminators which includes operators and brackets. Second, each string token is converted into a Token with type and value information.
